### GET /business/product/store

This endpoint retrieves the list of products available in the store.

#### Request

No request body is required for this endpoint.

#### Response

The response will be a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "",
  "products": [
    {
      "pricing": {
        "price": 0,
        "discountRate": 0,
        "discountCode": ""
      },
      "prodId": "",
      "storeId": "",
      "title": "",
      "description": "",
      "media": [
        {
          "mainImage": {
            "id": "",
