### Admin Email Endpoint

This endpoint allows the admin to send emails with optional attachments.

#### Request Body Parameters

- `email` (text): Emails to send mail to

- `message` (text): Text formatted in HTML

- `attachment` (file): (optional) Files to send as attachment

- `url` (text): (optional) URL of attachment

- `subject` (text): The caption of the email


#### Response

``` json
{
  "success": true,
  "msg": ""
}

 ```

#### JSON Schema

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "success": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "msg": {
      "type": "string"
    }
