### GET /business/store/store_category

This endpoint retrieves the list of store categories.

#### Request

This is a GET request to the endpoint `{{baseUrl}}/business/store/store_category`.

#### Response

The response is a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "success": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "msg": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "category": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string"
