request.description:
# Retrieve Shipping Address

This endpoint retrieves the shipping address for the shopper.

## Request

### Request Body

- title (string, required): The title of the address.

- street (string, required): The street of the address.

- phoneNumber (string, required): The phone number associated with the address.

- houseNumber (string, required): The house number of the address.

- city (string, required): The city of the address.

- state (string, required): The state of the address.

- status (string, required): The status of the address.


Example:

``` json
{
  "title": "Random Job Title",
  "street": "Random Street Address",
  "phoneNumber": "08120485768",
  "houseNumber": "Random Alpha Numeric",
  "city": "Random City",
  "state": "Random City",
  "status": "primary"
}

 ```

## Response

### 200 OK

- Content-Type: application/json


Example Response Body:

``` json
{
  "success": true,
  "msg": "",
  "data": [
    {
      "userId": "",
      "addressId": "",
      "title": "",
      "phoneNumber": "",
      "street": "",
      "houseNumber": "",
      "city": "",
      "state": "",
      "status": ""
    }
  ]
}

 ```

### JSON Schema

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "success": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "msg": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "userId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "addressId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "title": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "phoneNumber": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "street": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "houseNumber": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "city": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "state": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

