request.description:
The `GET` request to `/user/country_states` endpoint retrieves a list of states associated with a country. The response is in JSON format and has the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "success": {
            "type": "boolean"
        },
        "msg": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "state": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
                "type": "string"
            }
        }
    }
}

 ```

The endpoint retrieves the local government areas (LGAs) and senatorial districts within a specific state.

The response for this request can be documented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "success": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "msg": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "state": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "state": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "senatorial_districts": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        },
        "lgas": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

